snippet.title: Sonic: Fan Games/Hacks 14: One Girl Army (SAGE2005)
snippet.description:
(These are my simple game play videos)
(I can and will remove specific videos if its necessary/requested)

Name: One Girl Army
Credit: Clwe
Release Date: Possibly 2005

My Website: https://scaleyfoxy.weebly.com/

Download: http://dlxcaiman.net/dlx/OneGirlArmy.zip

00:00 = Main Menu+Intro
01:51 = Stage 1.1 Snow Land
04:32 = Stage 1.2 Ice Cave
08:18 = Stage 1.3 Flight
10:40 = Stage 2.1 Forest
13:50 = Stage 2.2 Ruins
17:57 = Stage 2.3 Boss (Egg Mobile-D)
20:04 = Stage 3.1 Desert
24:58 = Stage 3.2 Mountain
31:29 = Stage 3.3 Boss (Egg Frog)
34:34 = Stage 4.1 Castle (Outside)
41:43 = Stage 4.2 Castle (Inside)
48:27 = Stage 4.3 Final Boss (Egg Bomber Tank)
54:32 = Ending
56:58 = Credits

NOTES: One of the first Sonic Fangames i ever played and back in the day could never finish xD
One Amy Army!
